tests

Class ExportErrorCheckTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.ExportErrorCheckTest

  • public class ExportErrorCheckTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which extensively tests the ExportErrorCheck class. If given improper command orders, the application must determine that there is a problem with the given sequence of commands. This set of tests puts the responsible class under several scenarios to tests functionality.
    Since:
    2017-04-01
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Dilshad Khatri, Alvis Koshy, Drew Noel, Jonathan Tung
